Quote.create(:quote=>"E-mail clients physically move the e-mail from the e-mail server to your PC's hard drive. After the e-mail is downloaded, it no longer exists in the e-mail provider's network. The e-mail exists in your e-mail client program (on the PC's hard drive) until you delete it.", :score=> 0, :category_id=>43, :matchups => 0)
