Quote.create(:quote=>"When a woman asks a small favor of you, like hold her seat while she takes a call, you can say, \"Oh, I see...you're using me already! I bet you'd like to use me for a lot of things, wouldn't you?\" If she has an adult's IQ, she'll laugh, partly because it's a funny role reversal and partly because there's some truth in what you're saying. This is a great way to subtly introduce some low-pressure sexual tension into your conversation", :score=> 0, :category_id=>46, :matchups => 0)
