Quote.create(:quote=>"The familiar, inconspicuous front is the perfect smoke screen. Approach your mark with an idea that seems ordinary enough-a business deal, financial intrigue. The sucker's mind is distracted, his suspicions allayed. That is when you gently guide him onto the second path, the slippery slope down which he slides helplessly into your trap.", :score=> 0, :category_id=>49, :matchups => 0)
